summary:
This mod increases the number of enemies in Skyrim for increased challenge.
No required DLC.
MCM Available.
descriptionHtml: Enemizer uses a script method to spawn additional enemies. Certain basic enemies, such as bandits and wolves, will spawn another enemy of a similar type when they are loaded. For example, anywhere you would normally encounter one bandit, you will now encounter two bandits.  The mod also includes an MCM to adjust the number of enemies that spawn. No DLC is required.
author: carstenseng1
